{"product_id":"magrada-blueberry-tinted-lip-balm-10ml","title":"Magrada Blueberry Tinted Lip Balm 10ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis balm's delightful lightweight formula melts seamlessly into your lips, leaving behind a gorgeous blueberry hue and a radiant, natural shine. Embrace beauty while making a conscious choice—crafted from 100% vegan ingredients and wrapped in eco-friendly packaging, this balm is truly a beauty essential.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply to clean lips as desired. Perfect for use as a nourishing lip balm before applying lipstick or as a glossy finish over lip balm or lip liner.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eHydroxystearic\/Linolenic\/OleicPolyglycerides, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Polyglyceryl-3 Diisostearate, Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Candelilla Cera, Aroma (Flavor), CI 77019\/Mica, Dipalmitoyl Hydroxyproline, CI77163\/Bismuth Oxychloride, CI 77491\/Iron Oxide, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Stevia Rebaudiana (Sweetleaf) Extract\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 100%\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eparaben-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e sulphate-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e silicone-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e alcohol-free \u003cspan\u003e| EU allergen-free\u003c\/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e| \u003c\/span\u003evegan \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e cruelty-free \u003cspan\u003e| \u003c\/span\u003ewith a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50848777699655,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-blueberry-tinted-lip-balm-10ml-587083.png?v=1739897252","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/magrada-blueberry-tinted-lip-balm-10ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}